# Contributing Guidelines

Thank you for your interest in contributing to the Simple Interest Calculator project.

We welcome and appreciate all types of contributions. Whether you want to report a bug, fix an issue, improve documentation, suggest enhancements, or share new ideas â€” your input is valuable.

